text: (Ukhula isayino muburi bwabu) paparanga mbuemikanda(chiabasuku) chishili okhurula. Ne emikanda echo chitsanga ( khandi), bakhekombele mbu bakhabeele mushitsimi halala nende abamenyanwa bamwo (baduwi), barebasa amakhuwa kenyu, Ne babetsanga halala ninenyu shibakhakhupane tawe halali hatiti butswa
